do you think you get to live?

53:39.581 --> 53:41.284
What are you going to do?

53:41.317 --> 53:44.786
Keep starting over
and hoping that this time,

53:44.820 --> 53:48.091
what, you'll be different?

53:48.123 --> 53:51.426
The other person
will be different.

53:51.460 --> 53:53.195
The world will magically change

53:53.228 --> 53:56.698
