better for you.

53:56.731 --> 54:01.036
Whatever list you're keeping,
you better throw it out.

54:01.070 --> 54:03.972
It's not about
finding something new.

54:04.005 --> 54:08.277
It's about restoring something
that has been broken.

54:09.811 --> 54:12.447
It's about repair.

55:14.976 --> 55:16.778
When he comes home
the next time,

55:16.811 --> 55:19.449
you'll have to surprise him.

55:19.481 --> 55:22.784
