but at least we could leave.

55:59.954 --> 56:02.557
South Beach,
give me Miami.

56:02.590 --> 56:06.328
Give me sand,
lots of sand.

56:13.369 --> 56:16.838
"To be or not to be.

56:16.871 --> 56:20.175
That is the question.

56:20.208 --> 56:22.010
Whether 'tis nobler
