57:30.112 --> 57:32.148
We have to stop!

57:32.181 --> 57:34.750
But how do you stop it?

57:34.782 --> 57:37.619
What's the resolution?

57:37.652 --> 57:40.255
Where can one go from here?

57:40.289 --> 57:44.627
"Who would fardels bear,
to grunt and sweat

57:44.659 --> 57:48.364
