when they are.

01:04:15.583 --> 01:04:17.685
Now what does that say
about the fathering, huh?

01:04:17.719 --> 01:04:20.755
Is that the type of father
you'd imagined yourself to be,

01:04:20.789 --> 01:04:26.695
