01:04:41.576 --> 01:04:44.713
The word, the word is...

01:04:45.880 --> 01:04:48.717
The word is...

01:05:01.963 --> 01:05:03.798
- Contempt.
- I put in time.

01:05:03.831 --> 01:05:07.536
